                publication faster and easier than traditional methods. It‚Äôs ideal for club races with multiple
                series or overlapping events ‚Äî for example, a single race might count toward both a Low Wind Series,
                a Club Championship, and the August Series without duplicate entry.
            </p>
            <p>
