                    aria-controls="ans-different">
                What makes SailScores different from other scoring programs?
            </button>
        </h3>
        <div id="ans-different" class="collapse">
            <ul>
                <li>
                    Club-oriented rather than single-event focused. Competitors are entered once, and then shared
                    across series and seasons.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Fully web-based ‚Äî results are automatically published online, reducing steps for scorekeepers.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Mobile-friendly ‚Äî designed to work smoothly on phones and tablets without a keyboard for
                    scorekeepers as well viewers.
